{"type": "article", "id": 20800, "title": "雾霾，就这么改变了我的生活 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "时常感觉在演末日恐怖片。", "date": "2016-01-17T09:00:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4200, "name": "雾霾"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607120215RE5hrH0lsKFo7i1C.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 宅。（看片/书/综艺量显著增加。）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150609zAfrda0yGTIjxMlF.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.75090909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2. 宅的各种副作用。长胖。睡太多。效率低下。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120200YuzZt7UBeWNa3kXf.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562249\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3. 头痛。眼睛痛。嗓子痛。心痛。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120200DjJZsrw2YX3q8eLv.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.764\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>4. 更爱到家 app。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261506097sR3iU0SrmYG4oWx.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"gif\"><strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>5. 口罩永远放在购物车。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120201UJjGod40g8aCpSeI.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56385542\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6. 桌子上多个专门的位置放口罩。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120202KPy68JYoEOkCuQNM.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.84341085\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7. 为了空出耳朵每天只有一种发型是马尾。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120202ipePn9a6jVQd2LgR.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8. 外出没有颜值可言。但也没关系因为大家都一样。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120204c9NTnOZCePvYDX42.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.63965517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9. 不怕死的人脱颖而出：从不戴口罩，说你们至于吗？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120205op73lXxR8OLEWecV.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56289308\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10. 昏昏沉沉起不了床。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071202059gNJCBZ7rpdXQYfo.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.50333333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11. 拍寂静岭连特效都不需要。@阿西劳</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120206CbHYnTFmyN8jMarp.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.95090909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>12. 有一种新游戏是脑补建筑物。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120206klAf89FDuYGRdUHv.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.78718535\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13. 有空气净化器才有安全感。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120207vXA8crNEPBU20eZK.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.70140281\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14. 现在北京的朋友约饭局都是，哎，周末来我家吃饭吧，我家净化器是 blue air，另一个朋友说：我家 IQ air 啊，大家说：那还是去你家吃吧！ @苏更生</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120207Xr67weC8ZESzgxik.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>15. 多了一个不想去办公室的理由。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071202083PbmUQrKeN19Jxc5.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.5925\" data-format=\"gif\"><strong>16. 每天都在等风来。</strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150612IjDNwzfQFHmCb8ky.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"223\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.5575\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>17. 看到蓝天白云幸福得要流泪。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071202104Rv3PetI8WKg9Mu6.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.44\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18. 肺科医生在北京市中心买了小洋楼。@TM</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120210GjP1SO4WbMFtr7T0.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.864\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19. 现在晒老家都不提特产，提我们那 PM 多少多少。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120211Z2759LlDvr8NjHPg.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.532\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>20. 高考的同学选择城市多了个考虑项。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120212WstvyLic8g4oHVQ7.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.494\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>21. 买了一本《洛杉矶雾霾启示录》看书风格要与时俱进。@ 无法归类</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"> \r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120213xJUb48wKuPlTVHc6.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n\t</p>\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</span> \r\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n"}